room_title: Escape room "Skip Tracer" by Mind Games Clovis in Fresno
room_address: 30 W Shaw Ave, Suite 108 Clovis, CA 93612
room_description:
Travel in time to the 1940s with Skip Tracer. You’re meeting up with an old pal from school who’s now a private detective. Your buddy is missing, you are a suspect, and the Lindon Mob and the cops are hot on your trail. Save your friend and yourselves in this puzzle-filled room!
The difficulty level of the game can be modified to 35-40% success rate for beginners.
